data.description:
Welcome to this lovely and practical family home, perfect for creating lasting memories. Upon entering, you'll find a spacious open floor plan that seamlessly connects the great room and an amazing huge kitchen. This kitchen is a dream, complete with a breakfast bar, a cozy nook, a gas stove, granite counter tops, and ovens to satisfy your culinary aspirations. The custom 36'' ember glaze cabinets with custom rope design & nickel rope knobs, feature self-closing drawers, adding a touch of convenience to your daily routine.
With a thoughtful layout, this home offers two bedrooms and a bath that are perfect for children. Additionally, there's a separate bedroom and bath that can cater to a teenager or grandparent, ensuring privacy and flexibility. The primary bedroom suite is tucked away in the back of the house, providing a tranquil retreat. All bathrooms feature executive height vanities & raised toilets. Marble vanity counter tops in the master bathroom. This home boasts 2x6 construction, post tension foundation, sprayed foam insulation in the attic. Video doorbell, ADT alarm system, 12x24 tile floors throughout, with carpet in bedrooms. Plumbed for water softener. The AC settings and Irrigation can be controlled with your smart phone, making this home "smart", Keyless pad garage door opener & custom security front door are also featured.
For those who love to entertain, an elegant formal dining room awaits. Connected to the kitchen through a convenient butler's pantry, hosting dinners and celebrations will be a breeze. The dining room & kitchen features custom light fixtures.
But the real highlight of this home lies outside. A glass slider opens the wall completely, seamlessly merging your indoor and outdoor living spaces. Step outside to a huge, newly landscaped backyard (16,389 SF lot). Here, you'll find a Pebble sheen abalone diving pool with a pop-up self-cleaning system, perfect for relaxing or hosting poolside gatherings.
For those with boats, RVs, or work vehicles, an RV gate and parking on the side of the house provide ample space to accommodate your needs.
Don't miss the opportunity to experience this incredible home firsthand. Come visit and discover the perfect place to call home.
